dct_title_s: Map showing property lines along the Hudson River in Harrington Township, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Hand-drawn map showing the property lines along the Hudson River in Bergen County, New Jersey and boundary with Rockland County, New York
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
There are handwritten dates of years including 1872, 1873
